                       "description":  "Identifies when a privileged role is assigned to a new user. Any account eligible for a role is now being given privileged access. If the assignment is unexpected or into a role that isn\u0027t the responsibility of the account holder, investigate.\nPLATFORM:Azure AD,Microsoft 365,IaaS\nMITRE:TA0003;T1078;T1078.004;T1098;T1098.003,TA0004;T1078;T1078.004;T1098;T1098.003,TA0005;T1078;T1078.004",
